|WKBDexterity:                   Range: |YKB1-200
 
    |YKODexterity encompasses a number of physical attributes including
hand-eye coordination, agility, reflexes, balance, precision, and speed
of movement. Dexterity affects a character's accuracy with missile
weapons (darts, arrows, cats, etc.) and in the ability to swing weapons
at moving targets. Dexterity is also important for dodging attacks.
Dexterity is particularly important for roguish guilds which rely on
quick reflexes and the manipulation of small objects.
